            "description_expanded": true,
            "title_1": "Benefits",
            "icon_name_1": "",
            "raw_content_1": "<p><strong>Barrier‑friendly cleansing:</strong> pH‑balanced gentle surfactants and glycerin blend wash away makeup, oil and impurities without stripping your skin’s natural moisture barrier.<br/><br/><strong>Microbiome support:</strong> Prebiotic oat extract helps nurture a healthy skin microbiome, leaving your complexion calm and resilient.<br/><br/><strong>Multi‑use convenience:</strong> One bottle replaces six products— use it as a makeup remover, facial cleanser, body wash, hand soap, bubble bath or shaving gel.<br/><br/><strong>Gentle for all:</strong> Dermatologist‑tested,  clinically proven to be safe for sensitive skin, kids and during pregnancy. <br/><br/><strong>Sustainable & ethical:</strong> Vegan, cruelty‑free and free from sulfates, silicones, parabens, phthalates and microplastics. Packaged in refillable, recyclable bottles produced in a carbon‑neutral facility, with a portion of proceeds supporting plastic recovery. </p>",
            "title_2": "Key Ingredients",
            "icon_name_2": "",
            "raw_content_2": "<p><strong>Glycerin: </strong>A humectant that attracts and retains moisture, helping to keep skin soft and hydrated while protecting the natural moisture barrier.</p><p><strong>Aloe</strong>: A classic skin‑soother beloved for its ability to calm, hydrate and replenish. </p><p><strong>Gentle Surfactants:</strong> Mild, plant‑derived surfactants that lift away impurities without disrupting the skin’s pH or microbiome.</p><p><strong>Gntl Signature Fragrance</strong>: A warm yet fresh gender-neutral scent developed to be safe for sensitive skin </p><p>All ingredients are vegan and cruelty‑free. The formula contains <strong>no sulfates, silicones, parabens, phthalates, PEGs or microplastics</strong>.</p><p>Full ingredients: Water (Aqua), Sodium Methyl Oleoyl Taurate, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Lauryl Glucoside, Coco-Glucoside, Fragrance (Parfum), Glycerin, Sodium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Linalool, Limonene, Geraniol, Citral.</p>",
            "title_3": "How to Use",
            "icon_name_3": "",
            "raw_content_3": "<p>Apply to wet hands, washcloth, or loofa and massage lather onto damp skin. Rinse thoroughly with warm water. </p><p>Skin Wash is tough enough to remove daily makeup and SPF, but if you wear waterproof mascara, consider using an oil-based cleanser, then follow with Skin Wash. </p>",
            "title_4": "Packaging",
            "icon_name_4": "",
            "raw_content_4": "<p>Skin Wash is housed in aluminum bottles, a material that is infinitely recyclable. It features a food-grade liner that serves as an alternative to typical BPA liners, ensuring the product remains safe and stable.</p><p>The pump is the only component that cannot be recycled, so please treat it with care by refilling and reusing your bottle multiple times before recycling.</p><p>Our refill pouch is made with minimal material from a bio-based, carbon negative source that's recyclable in your local #4 stream, making our entire packaging system environmentally responsible from start to finish.</p>",
            "title_5": "",
            "icon_name_5": "",
            "raw_content_5": "",
            "padding_bottom": 20
          }
        },
