    "section_faq_4mrHcA": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_V3abL8": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "What is Skin Wash used for?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Skin Wash and what makes it different from a regular body wash?",
            "content": "<p>Skin Wash is a 6-in-1 multi-use cleanser formulated to facial-grade standards, meaning it’s gentle enough for your face, yet effective enough to replace your body wash, hand soap, makeup remover, shaving gel, and bubble bath. </p><p>Most body washes are formulated for body skin only and use harsh sulfates that can strip moisture. Skin Wash soap-free, uses baby-safe surfactants, is pH-balanced, and is free from sulfates, silicones, parabens, phthalates, and alcohols for a gentle yet effective cleanse. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_w3ncCf": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it a facial cleanser or body wash?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does it actually remove makeup and SPF?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Wash is formulated to effectively remove makeup, including foundation and mascara, as well as SPF. For waterproof eye makeup, we recommend using a dedicated makeup remover first.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_gWBybL": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it safe for sensitive skin?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does it smell like?",
            "content": "<p>Skin Wash has a clean, grounding scent — bright orange blossom and marjoram with grounding sandalwood. It's cleanly formulated, and free from potential irritants like essential oils and phthalates. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_8VE3Fe": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Does it remove makeup?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Skin Wash safe for sensitive skin?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Was has passed clinical testing on a panel of sensitive skin. It uses baby-safe surfactants, is pH-balanced, and is free from known irritants including sulfates, artificial dyes, and synthetic fragrance allergens regulated by EU standards. </p><p>However, if you are sensitive to fragrance, we recommend waiting for our fragrance-free version. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_fArmLD": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it safe during pregnancy and for kids?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Skin Wash safe during pregnancy, postpartum, and for kids?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Wash was deigned for the every life stage and for the whole family. It is formulated without ingredients of concern for pregnancy, including retinoids, salicylic acid, and certain essential oils.</p><p>If using on young children or infants, we recommend checking with your pediatrician. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_ezhJbm": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "How long does a bottle last?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does one bottle last?",
            "content": "<p>With full-body daily use, a 16.9oz bottle typically lasts 5–6 weeks. The 33.8oz Refill Pouch lasts approximately 3–4 months for the same use pattern.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
